{"tid":1108622,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃心美暗寸馬國明老：唔用年過半百已好好","createTime":"2019-04-16T05:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T06:29:02.000Z","uid":5077,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50827e9c080f535078d97495a005a13551a34263","tid":1108622,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"藝人黃心穎與胞姐黃心美出席電訊活動，兩人在台上演出趣劇，在劇中，心美自爆有男友，又狠狠地拍了心穎的頭一下。<br />\n<br />\n接受訪問時，記者笑指心穎出嫁就會搬出去，心美坦言妹妹今年才28歲，有想過28歲結婚是否太早：「我唔介意佢爬我頭，我婚都離埋。我當年結婚都係28歲，以我經驗嚟講，唔好28歲就結婚，我當初結婚都唔知為乜，等佢腦囟生埋先。」<span style=\"color: red;\">記者指男方已經一把年紀，不能等太久，心美即抵死地說：「你哋唔用年過半百呢個字已經好好。」</span>心穎直言結婚不應受年齡限制，亦難計劃太多。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/jacqueline-wong-4-sisters/screen-shot-2017-01-13-at-01-02-07/21610599-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2017-01-13-At-01-02-07_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Fjacqueline-wong-4-sisters%2Fscreen-shot-2017-01-13-at-01-02-07%2F21610599-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2017-01-13-At-01-02-07_img_885_590.jpg&h=9dee8e37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47d50fbb14cfd7c280fd8170152627f754867ee4","tid":1108622,"uid":165817,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"佢兩姊妹真係好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會有人話黃心美靚 成個人乾巫婆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c847b7e9a1ad26ee32b878a6e140f3bd0985b160","tid":1108622,"uid":61724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"最細果個最正"},{"pid":"14d21ec5a796c029f7f2ab2f2b49f60e5f1dc352","tid":1108622,"uid":155682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:27:02.000Z","msg":"如果馬明都年過半百, 老鼠安咪花甲之年?"},{"pid":"70233f379e4be14bccc8b51b3c2a38fa989e7c05","tid":1108622,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47d5